      "listing": {
        "id": "8c64c260-c232-4b34-b8c6-70483e6a3586",
        "title": "\ud83d\udd10\u26a1 Privacy Track \u2014 Colosseum Hackathon (Powered by MagicBlock, ST MY & SNS)",
        "slug": "privacy-track-colosseum-hackathon-powered-by-magicblock-st-my-and-sns",
        "description": "<p class=\"text-node\">Privacy is the primitive for the next generation of on-chain applications \u2014 especially in a world of autonomous agents.<br><br>This track challenges you to build privacy-first systems on Solana, powered by <strong>MagicBlock's (Private) Ephemeral Rollups &amp; Payment API</strong>:</p><ul class=\"list-node\"><li><p class=\"text-node\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://docs.magicblock.gg/pages/ephemeral-rollups-ers/how-to-guide/quickstart\">Ephemeral Rollup</a> (ER)</p></li></ul><ul class=\"list-node\"><li><p class=\"text-node\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://docs.magicblock.gg/pages/private-ephemeral-rollups-pers/how-to-guide/quickstart\">Private Ephemeral Rollup</a> (PER)</p></li><li><p class=\"text-node\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://docs.magicblock.gg/pages/private-ephemeral-rollups-pers/api-reference/per/introduction\">Private Payments API</a></p></li></ul><p class=\"text-node\"><br>\ud83d\udc49 Think beyond wallets and balances \u2014 build systems where data, intent, and interactions remain private by default, while still being composable and verifiable.<br><br>\u2e3b<br><br><strong>\ud83e\udde0 What we're looking for: Frontier Projects</strong></p><ul class=\"list-node\"><li><p class=\"text-node\">Private payments &amp; shielded transactions</p></li><li><p class=\"text-node\">Private DeFi (Auctions, Lending, Trading primitives)</p></li><li><p class=\"text-node\">Agentic commerce, Agent-to-agent, x402 APIs, MPP etc</p></li><li><p class=\"text-node\">and more ... find more ideas in our database for <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://www.notion.so/24fc5a1ab4d68034988ae014fed28600?v=24fc5a1ab4d680b7b11d000c877544ec\">RFPs</a>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"text-node\"><br>\u2e3b<br><br><strong>\u26a1 Why Solana and Magicblock</strong></p><ul class=\"list-node\"><li><p class=\"text-node\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://docs.magicblock.gg/pages/ephemeral-rollups-ers/introduction/why\">Low latency, zero fees at scale</a></p></li><li><p class=\"text-node\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://docs.magicblock.gg/pages/private-ephemeral-rollups-pers/introduction/onchain-privacy\">Privacy, composability and security</a></p></li><li><p class=\"text-node\">Regulatory <a target=\"\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://docs.magicblock.gg/pages/private-ephemeral-rollups-pers/introduction/compliance-framework\">compliance</a> and control</p></li><li><p class=\"text-node\">Built-in onchain <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://docs.magicblock.gg/pages/tools/crank/introduction\">automation</a> and <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://docs.magicblock.gg/pages/templates/random-character-generator\">randomness</a></p></li><li><p class=\"text-node\">Ready-to-Use <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://docs.magicblock.gg/pages/private-ephemeral-rollups-pers/api-reference/per/introduction\">Private Payment API</a></p></li></ul><p class=\"text-node\"><br>\u2e3b<br><br><strong>\ud83c\udfc6 Prize Breakdown (Total: $5,000)</strong></p><ul class=\"list-node\"><li><p class=\"text-node\">\ud83e\udd47 1st Place \u2014 $2,500</p></li><li><p class=\"text-node\">\ud83e\udd48 2nd Place \u2014 $1,500</p></li><li><p class=\"text-node\">\ud83e\udd49 3rd Place \u2014 $1,000</p></li></ul><p class=\"text-node\"><br>\u2e3b<br><br><strong>\ud83d\udee0\ufe0f Judging Criteria</strong></p><p class=\"text-node\"><strong>Technology (40%)</strong></p><ul class=\"list-node\"><li><p class=\"text-node\">Effective use of ER, PER, or Private Payments API</p></li><li><p class=\"text-node\">Working demo</p></li><li><p class=\"text-node\">Quality of architecture and smart contract design</p></li></ul><p class=\"text-node\"><strong>Impact (30%)</strong></p><ul class=\"list-node\"><li><p class=\"text-node\">Solves a real-world problem</p></li><li><p class=\"text-node\">Clear market need</p></li><li><p class=\"text-node\">Potential for adoption and monetization</p></li></ul><p class=\"text-node\"><strong>Creativity &amp; UX (30%)</strong></p><ul class=\"list-node\"><li><p class=\"text-node\">Novel primitives, mechanisms, or UX</p></li><li><p class=\"text-node\">Smooth user experience</p></li><li><p class=\"text-node\">Clarity of how the system works</p></li></ul><p class=\"text-node\"></p><p class=\"text-node\">\u2e3b</p><p class=\"text-node\"></p><p class=\"text-node\"><strong>\u2705 Submission Requirements</strong></p><ul class=\"list-node\"><li><p class=\"text-node\"><strong>Working demo: </strong>Live deployment with successful MagicBlock integration</p></li><li><p class=\"text-node\"><strong>Code repository (GitHub):</strong> Publicly accessible</p></li><li><p class=\"text-node\"><strong>Short demo video (3 min)</strong>: Problem \u2192 Solution \u2192 Demo</p></li></ul><p class=\"text-node\"><br>\u2e3b</p><p class=\"text-node\"><br><strong>\ud83d\udc49 Bring privacy to Solana \u2014 with MagicBlock.</strong></p><p class=\"text-node\"></p>",
